				<td colspan="2"><span>You do not need a raid to kill either of the mobs that drop this: Monstrous Sea Turtle or Ferrocious Barracuda. They're both fully slowable and if you're in the EP's then one grouping should be right up your ally. Maybe take a few extra friends along for healing/dps if you haven't been in the EP's long; but your tanks sound like they'll do fine. iirc. Any of the mobs that drop pet weapons are one groupable... they may be extremely rare spawns (like this one) and have really rare drops, but they're all one groupable.
<br />

<br />
As for DPS , I dunno =( I still haven't gotten mine, after being EP flagged for over a year. Most people don't like grouping in Water 'cause it's a pain.. much like they didn't like too much of Kedge Keep and Siren's Grotto back in the day. Both mobs are placeholder spawns. The turtle usually spawns in the first cavern.. I've heard from any turtle and I've also heard from any &quot;greater&quot; turtle. The barracuda I've seen in the next cavern on the right, same deal.. i've heard any barracuda and only &quot;greater&quot; barracuda's.
<br />

<br />
I believe it procs little swords with blue music notes, though don't quote me on that.
<br />

<br />
Be warned, you will probably get MIGHT tired of seeing the Coral Shard enchanter piece drop. =)</span></td>
